reviewText: The stories were good, not what I expected but I still watched most of them have a few more left.
Quality Lifetime entertainment at an extraordinarily low price!
good for a rainy Sunday afternoon....the story based on the girl helping the Jews during WWII was moving and made me appreciate all she and others did to help the Jews
some better then others, but very much worth the cost.
Its okay.... some of the movies where okay and others were good....
Always love the Lifetime movies.  Great collection, and price.
